Title: Spinning Car Cat Toy
Body (HTML): Breakfast is served for the hipster kitty in your life! The adorable Quirky Kitty Avocado Toast 2 pack cat toys are purrfect for all hip cats and kittens! Filled with tempting catnip and silvervine (always pure and pesticide-free), and fun crinkly paper for engaging sound.
